{"tid":1835440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎：港人自救措施","createTime":"2020-01-23T00:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T01:26:28.000Z","uid":311358,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"66e747bb8764ab6ba9bc32ea86d1a5f9dec9b20d","tid":1835440,"uid":311358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T00:33:58.000Z","msg":"幾樣野必須第一時間做，唔好等濕鳩禍港林鄭<br />\n<br />\n1）個人：帶口罩、勤洗手；任何不適請即休假、有流感肺炎病徵立即求醫<br />\n<br />\n2）物業管理處：所有職員、外判全部戴口罩工作；電梯、大堂數小時定時消毒，每日更換升降機𨋢制膠貼<br />\n<br />\n3）入境處：封鎖內地進出關口，停飛內地<br />\n<br />\n4）醫管局：提升醫護人員防疫級數<br />\n<br />\n5）教育局：幼兒、學前教育立即停課，中小學分批停課<br />\n<br />\n6）庫務局：拒絕所有災害捐款申請<br />\n<br />\n7）警務處：收回暴動定性<br />\n<br />\n8）律政司：撤銷抗爭者控罪<br />\n<br />\n9）行政會議：成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n10）行政長官：林鄭下台<br />\n<br />\n11）立法會：實行真雙普選"},{"pid":"9fc6b8d30c8703ba7630efd63f7d8d31ec05702d","tid":1835440,"uid":53026,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:00:26.000Z","msg":"永久取消單程證，支那人回鄉永久定居"},{"pid":"70e6465ca7aadae75d5643334ee65c7e04918521","tid":1835440,"uid":233009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T03:03:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fb99bd501bdb9f844c1b1f05a608024223a861fa","tid":1835440,"uid":78762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T03:33:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4e0d5a6f6e631365bbfad2cbc5562d709df44738","tid":1835440,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T03:34:11.000Z","msg":"【第廿叄期牆紙x民記】黃色經濟起革命 良心消費衛我城<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1833670/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1833670/page/1</a><br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=5896f683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=